{"tid":975434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林子健涉嫌向警員虛報被擄走案　裁判官裁定表證成立","createTime":"2019-01-09T15:29:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T15:29:57.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9ce4cc325e27a1d8d145fd5dfd5631d78d77680d","tid":975434,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2017/08/%E7%91%AA%E9%BA%97%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2-%E6%9E%97%E5%AD%90%E5%81%A5-20170811131903_20fb_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2017%2F08%2F%25E7%2591%25AA%25E9%25BA%2597%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%2581%25A5-20170811131903_20fb_large.jpg&h=7386adda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主黨成員林子健涉嫌向警員虛報被擄走的案件，裁判官裁定表面證供成立。<br />\n<br />\n控方傳召的法醫病理學專家作供時說，相信林子健肚皮和大腿傷痕，由他自己造成。<br />\n<br />\n辯方傳召的英國法醫反駁，控方所說的是一般指標，並非經診斷後確定林子健屬於自殘。"}]}